{"tid":2509705,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[美國大選] 2021美國人口普查：德州選舉人票+2，加州伊州紐約州-1","createTime":"2021-04-29T15:33:11.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-29T15:45:56.000Z","uid":52658,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c97bc4f6f8c33e9c046ea984951df5fe87562948","tid":2509705,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T15:33:11.000Z","msg":"因疫情及國內政局動盪，美國人口普查局（US Census Bureau）原定4月1日便會公布「2020年人口普查」調查，延至26日釋出。結果顯示，全美人口總數雖來到3億3144萬9281人，但十年來的人口成長率7.4%（2010-20年），卻創下有史以來第二低點，增幅僅高於1930年代大蕭條時期。<br />\n<br />\n於此同時，這份報告也攸關美國大選選舉人團票數計算，國會眾議院席次，便是每十年隨著的各州人口比例來分配（總席次固定435席）。因此根據調查結果，明年美國期中選舉前，由共和黨主導的德州（TX）便會增加2個國會席次、至38席。以民主黨支持者占多數的紐約州及加州，則將各減1席。<br />\n<br />\n美國選舉人票計法：州眾議院議席+2<br />\n<br />\n德州+2<br />\n佛州+1<br />\n北卡羅萊納州+1<br />\n蒙大拿州+1<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n加州-1<br />\n紐州-1<br />\n伊州-1<br />\n賓州-1<br />\n密西根州-1<br />\n威斯康辛州-1<br />\n維吉尼亞州-1<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmcLTZuLLHQK9gE6Rh54YBkFon8LvMuUnXjST4qkNok6Fo?filename=ErjcxMM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FErjcxMM.png&h=44196ec5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n舊年大選結果<br />\n今次加既都係紅州為主<br />\n減既全部都係藍州<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">2024 Trump <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nMake America Great Again <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"be6aa8551d74224bfdde77bd54741216eed5a741","tid":2509705,"uid":303977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T15:36:40.000Z","msg":"因為藍人走咗去紅州<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n自己玩爛自己州 而家走去搞鳩其他州"},{"pid":"5ca58092d65197df2f48bd21cc8ebba238c07e1f","tid":2509705,"uid":52658,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"be6aa8551d74224bfdde77bd54741216eed5a741","tid":2509705,"uid":303977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T15:36:40.000Z","msg":"因為藍人走咗去紅州<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n自己玩爛自己州 而家走去搞鳩其他州"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T15:43:18.000Z","msg":"分散加州d藍票都係好事<br />\n今屆共和黨輸眾院既原因 係因為加州輸太多<br />\n7:3咁輸"},{"pid":"cee5e98f9889b7efc710f9e459e9a1a6117f85ef","tid":2509705,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T15:45:56.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\"><strong><span class=\"xx-large\">Young Man<br />\nThat no need feel down<br />\nI said Young Man<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span>"}]}